%% Part-out import — loading & fetch states (client UI)
%% Sources: docs/view-specs/part-out-import.md#loading--fetch-states,
%%          docs/view-specs/new-session.md#submit-outcomes-unit-1 (create-time fetch error → import)

stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> Loading: "view mount GET .../part-out/lines"
    Loading --> Ready: lines loaded
    Loading --> Retrying: "network error (auto retry up to 3)"
    Retrying --> Ready: retry success
    Retrying --> ErrorState: "retries exhausted or non-network failure"
    ErrorState --> Retrying: user taps Refetch
    Ready --> Ready: "manual refetch success (preserves exclusions)"

    note right of Loading
        Spinner shown. Exclude and Confirm disabled.
        Entry from New session create with
        partOutFetchStatus=error also starts here
        (zero lines until refetch succeeds)
    end note

    note right of Ready
        Included count at least 1 enables Confirm.
        Included count 0 disables Confirm.
    end note

    note right of ErrorState
        Empty table and Refetch button.
        Footer actions disabled until success.
    end note
